OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1773765957
OL,3,CPrisoner appears in court charged with
OL,4,Cmurder of child-killer Ian Huntley
OL,6,FA prison inmate has appeared in court
OL,7,Fcharged with the murder of child-
OL,8,Fkiller Ian Huntley.
OL,10,FAnthony Russell, 43, appeared via
OL,11,Fvideolink for a five-minute hearing at
OL,12,FNewton Aycliffe Magistrates' Court,
OL,13,FCounty Durham, on Wednesday 11 March.
OL,15,FWearing a grey sweatshirt and sitting
OL,16,Fat a table, he spoke only to confirm
OL,17,Fhis name and that he understood that
OL,18,Fhe will appear at Newcastle Crown
OL,19,FCourt on Thursday.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/7
