PN,42802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1773765957
OL,3,CPrisoner appears in court charged with
OL,4,Cmurder of child-killer Ian Huntley
OL,6,FRussell, who is from Coventry, is
OL,7,Fcharged with a single offence of
OL,8,Fmurdering the 52-year-old.
OL,10,FDistrict Judge Steven Hood told him:
OL,11,F"The offence of murder can only be
OL,12,Fheard in the crown court. Therefore I
OL,13,Fam sending this matter to Newcastle
OL,14,FCrown Court and you will appear at
OL,15,FNewcastle Crown Court tomorrow morning.
OL,26,@sD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/7
