PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1773765957
OL,3,CPrisoner appears in court charged with
OL,4,Cmurder of child-killer Ian Huntley
OL,6,F"The reason for that is because in
OL,7,Fmatters such as murder, the
OL,8,Fmagistrates' court cannot consider
OL,9,Fanything other than a remand in
OL,10,Fcustody, and the law states that a
OL,11,Fperson must appear within 48 hours
OL,12,Fbefore a crown court."
OL,14,FHuntley was reportedly attacked with a
OL,15,Fmetal bar in a workshop at HMP
OL,16,FFrankland near Durham, on 26 February.
OL,18,FThe 52-year-old was taken to the Royal
OL,19,FVictoria Infirmary, in Newcastle,
OL,20,Ffollowing the incident.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@VO]
