PN,42804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1773765957
OL,3,CPrisoner appears in court charged with
OL,4,Cmurder of child-killer Ian Huntley
OL,6,FHe remained on life support for more
OL,7,Fthan a week and, according to The Sun
OL,8,Fnewspaper, had been left blind from
OL,9,Fthe assault.
OL,11,FIt was previously reported that the
OL,12,Fmachines keeping him alive had been
OL,13,Fswitched off on Friday after brain
OL,14,Ftests showed he was in a vegetative
OL,15,Fstate. He was confirmed dead on
OL,16,FSaturday 7 March.
OL,18,FThe ex-school caretaker was serving a
OL,19,Flife sentence at the maximum security
OL,20,Fjail for the 2002 murders of 10-year-
OL,21,Folds Holly Wells and Jessica Chapman.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
