PN,42805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1773765957
OL,3,CPrisoner appears in court charged with
OL,4,Cmurder of child-killer Ian Huntley
OL,6,FHuntley, who was originally from
OL,7,FGrimsby, had served 23 years of his
OL,8,Fsentenced having been jailed in 2003.
OL,9,FAt the time he was told he would spend
OL,10,Fat least 40 years behind bars.
OL,12,FHe was found guilty of murdering Soham
OL,13,Fschoolgirls Holly and Jessica after
OL,14,Fthey left a barbecue to buy some
OL,15,Fsweets in August 2002.
OL,17,FHuntley was known to the girls because
OL,18,Fhe lived with Maxine Carr, a teaching
OL,19,Fassistant at their primary school.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/7
