OL,3,CPrisoner appears in court charged with
OL,4,Cmurder of child-killer Ian Huntley
OL,6,FFollowing his conviction, an inquiry
OL,7,Fled by Lord Michael Bichard found
OL,8,Fserious flaws in the way potential
OL,9,Femployees were vetted to work with
OL,10,Fchildren and vulnerable people.
OL,12,FThe review brought about major changes
OL,13,Fin the vetting and barring system, and
OL,14,Fled to the creation of a national
OL,15,Fintelligence database which enabled
OL,16,Fpolice to share information about
OL,17,Fsuspects.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/7
